name: Car Decal to Benefit Parson Blue
description:
All proceeds from this decal will go to benefit the Herrington Family to help with any needs they may have.  You can read about Parson Blue's story here. http://blueclark756.blogspot.com

Thanks so much for your donation for Parson Blue!! 

**When you check out in paypal if you are local and will be picking up the decal please be sure select "store pickup" in the shipping options.
